{"tid":574703,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【年底實測】中國製超音速飛機 北京飛紐約僅2小時","createTime":"2018-02-27T15:29:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-01T08:55:05.000Z","uid":28366,"like":4,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"09bffabe0dd59e821044a26b80bde51543865e5f","tid":574703,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T15:29:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/27/232851_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F27%2F232851_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=f62d4c30&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中國宣稱研製出一款超音速飛機「I-plane」，最高時速達每小時8,600公里，日後由北京飛到紐約，<span style=\"color: red;\">航程僅需2小時</span>，最快今年底衝上雲霄，進行實測。<br />\n<br />\n這項航天計劃由中國科學院在最新一期的《中國科學：物理學、力學、天文學》公布，這款已應用於中國軍事的機種，正向民航機市場邁進，讓長途飛行更方便。由研發員崔凱（Cui Kai）領導的團隊表示，該款客機時速可達6,115公里，快一般商用機6倍。該院又透露，已經在風洞測試過它的模型樣本，飛機最高速更可達每小時8,600公里，預言最快今年底試飛。<br />\n<br />\n研製超音速飛機成大國之間的實力較勁。英、法國早年曾合作研發「協和號」（Concorde），以不足3.5小時由巴黎飛紐約，成功載人運行廿多年後，其中一班機於2000年失事墜毀，釀成百多人死，「協和號」逐漸退出服役。近年，美國波音和洛歇馬田（Lockheed Martin）也積極研發新一代超音速偵察和攻擊機種。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180227/57881692\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180227%2F57881692&d=UZDbKUY8Pr2qvx8bfNpBpzCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=f23de07f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180227%2F57881692&h=7e20b800\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180227/57881692</a>"},{"pid":"79c8337fa56566af290183ed99c45d1851c8f787","tid":574703,"uid":28366,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T15:32:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95b9fe279c66c7fd94de6c4968b34ca949ec1238","tid":574703,"uid":27146,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T15:37:10.000Z","msg":"遲左50年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc80aff0df45b66823e2c43c61433bdd317d4700","tid":574703,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"95b9fe279c66c7fd94de6c4968b34ca949ec1238","tid":574703,"uid":27146,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T15:37:10.000Z","msg":"遲左50年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T15:38:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d16f55e239ef294ff9e8d86d24418872434a64b4","tid":574703,"uid":172128,"like":39,"dislike":0,"score":39,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T15:41:03.000Z","msg":"北京飛紐約僅2小時<br />\n北京飛地獄僅2秒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1e249bd283b87bcd175949d9dde116a0bbfda3e","tid":574703,"uid":83177,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T15:41:51.000Z","msg":"落地獄仲快， 可能唔使五分鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f3e16811cbd2777803a535358b8b7f278488734","tid":574703,"uid":28366,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c1e249bd283b87bcd175949d9dde116a0bbfda3e","tid":574703,"uid":83177,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T15:41:51.000Z","msg":"落地獄仲快， 可能唔使五分鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T15:49:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90008429433c05f4eacb6866822730f37908872f","tid":574703,"uid":170044,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T15:53:49.000Z","msg":"無事一問，其實到時真係有超音速飛機，搭既話會唔會有咩後遺症/副作用？頭暈果d"},{"pid":"88b37e55555ce875d94cc37dd9a52d0d0ec09dcf","tid":574703,"uid":162043,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":